{"tid":1440553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣入嚟】賤蓄亂放催淚彈，空氣污染如北京毒霾","createTime":"2019-08-10T12:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:51:33.000Z","uid":67045,"like":84,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f54e6cb9bebd188be3831b4a9b42a93879be3ab1","tid":1440553,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">分分鐘毒過北京霧霾<br />\n長期吸入好撚快會死<br />\n<br />\n其實已經唔係黃藍問題<br />\n無論你係咩政見<br />\n都應該推「阻止警察再放催淚彈】<br />\n<br />\n如果孕婦吸咗<br />\n分分鐘會流產會畸形<br />\n<br />\n小朋友吸咗會影響個腦<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n本身香港咁多樓、空氣流通咁差<br />\n空氣中嘅懸浮粒子會停留好耐<br />\n放一日<br />\n分分鐘要幾個月先散晒<br />\n<br />\n你老味依家日日放<br />\n仲要18區都放<br />\n啲空氣一樣差<br />\n啲空氣點吸得入去肺啊</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4f7fd72109c2939f21596a18cda389c349031f96","tid":1440553,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fba9c57c6d3d48ed79b36f5b94ff9a86838e323c","tid":1440553,"uid":62776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:52:35.000Z","msg":"幫你手推<br />\n黑警令空氣污染指數劇增<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc17fc4e30deaffb2b43d35f25bb51eb83e738b","tid":1440553,"uid":67045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">還我清新空氣！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e118e02d7d5921b3d90bcd86656e8b0198bf84f6","tid":1440553,"uid":67045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:55:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無論藍黃，都要呼吸！<br />\n我唔要聞化學毒氣！</span>"},{"pid":"59e5d359f69acbd1164db8932468465b12a9d790","tid":1440553,"uid":24443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:56:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭西 我都想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0383d14bae542eada4b57bccb6570a6fcb2f72","tid":1440553,"uid":67045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"